data.description: Terrific home located near the popular Powers Corridor, minutes from Peterson and Schriever AFB. The features include an open floor plan, generously-sized master suite master, convenient one-car attached garage, and enclosed backyard patio. The three bedrooms are situated on the upper level, along with a dedicated laundry space for added convenience.  The well-equipped kitchen features stainless steel appliances, rich cabinets, and overlooks the family room. The home has warm, neutral colors throughout. Additionally, the townhome is conveniently located walking distance to dog park and new shopping center with a market, dining, and shops.
